text.section:
In making the appointments, the Governor shall:
ensure that each geographic region of the State is represented;
ensure that various disciplines within the workers' compensation community are represented, including:
business;
labor;
the insurance industry;
the vocational rehabilitation industry;
the medical profession;
claimants' bar; and
defense bar; and
consider, in consultation with the chairman, the recommendations made by representatives of each of these disciplines.
